{"tid":2305383,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府刊憲要求曾到3間食肆人士周四前強制檢測","createTime":"2020-11-29T14:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T15:17:59.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"14f3ac5f1ae8a31af952e66a1fef74279f0d20b7","tid":2305383,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:47:39.000Z","msg":"政府刊憲，引用預防及控制疾病規例，要求於11月15日至11月29日期間，曾到過灣仔駱克道星月居、中環歷山大廈「Otto e Mezzo 8&frac12; BOMBANA」及上環誠信大廈泉章居大飯店的人士，須於12月3日或之前接受病毒檢測，並於12月6日或之前，向政府報告檢測結果或提交檢測報告，相關人士如在11月24日至29日期間已進行測試，均會視為已遵從強制檢測；檢測人士可到121間郵政局或醫管局47間指定普通科門診索取樣本包，或自行到衛生署認可私營化驗所、社區檢測中心、流動採樣亭及醫管局任何醫療設施接受檢測。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2368516\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2368516&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=bb2c44b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2368516</a>"},{"pid":"9dab7ecc41ec3778078458c1ff88f814efdf8b4e","tid":2305383,"uid":126731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"仲以為有乜咁把砲.....原來咁樣叫人去驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n30000 POPO狗仲未出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedcaf0cd601138b680225eba8c4688df410d62a","tid":2305383,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96ff9430c87e4b161af4edcebecfd8896d51add","tid":2305383,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2